relation: Another Mr. Saturn that I whipped up. I think it turned out fairly well, probably better than my previous versions.
Another old pic that was taking up space on my harddrive. I'd meant to do more to it, but I liked the energy it has already and was never sure how to go about improving it.

Another one of those enemies I previously just wasn't sure how I could tackle and make interesting. However, I think I may have plagarized the idea from someone around the site for the greenish drool stuff (not sure WHO though, if anyone... maybe it was such a great idea I figure it MUST have been someone else's...). :/ The tastebuds texture was a last minute addition, but I thought it really helped the picture overall in the end.
Another pic done while I was in Giygas mode.
Another pic of Frankstein MK II. I did this one without looking at reference material, but I think it turned out okay anyway.
